path.title: Oregon
path.desc: Oregon, nicknamed the Beaver State, became the thirty-third state in the US in 1859. It is the tenth largest state. The capital of Oregon is Salem. The accessible SVG viewer is being developed at ViewPlus Technologies in Corvallis, which is about 45 minutes south of Salem.
